ynthetic_Software/12765410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchemrxiv.org%2Farticles%2Fpreprint%2FReinforcing_the_Supply_Chain_of_COVID-19_Therapeutics_with_Expert-Coded_Retrosynthetic_Software%2F12765410&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=07aa72c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chemrxiv.org/articles/preprint/Reinforcing_the_Supply_Chain_of_COVID-19_Therapeutics_with_Expert-Coded_Retrosynthetic_Software/12765410</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:36:35.000Z","msg":"乜今次咁早啊外國勢力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de2a043854e2157216b7692559e3e8a89eba64f","tid":2146002,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:44:11.000Z","msg":"地塞米松好似係類固醇既一種？<br />\n我以前皮膚生野去睇醫生，開過地塞米松藥膏比我，一試即見效"},{"pid":"f5cc63d2384cfe379dc40993695153ab3c143392","tid":2146002,"uid":38861,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a119d97a790ac7ba689795e4d6ee0bcdfd612ea","tid":2146002,"uid":185985,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7e8ffa763db38fc4e8ba2bc59381b5c453c3c605","tid":2146002,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:25:55.000Z","msg":"歸立治理武肺的手段，現時可分為<span class=\"blue\">疫苗</span>、<span class=\"green\">人造抗體</span>、<span class=\"red\">藥物</span>以及<span class=\"gold\">各式化合物</span>四大手段。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">疫苗</span>具「長遠」預防作用，但不能醫治已受感染的病人，而且年長人士亦有可能基於免疫系統已甚為衰退關係，沒能被疫苗誘導身體製造充夠份量的抗體。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\">人造抗體</span>具有短期的預防及醫治效果，不受年齡界別所限，但預防的期限顯然會比疫苗為短。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">藥物</span>「理論上」沒有預防效用，但帶有醫治效果，暫時具認可能醫治武肺的藥物為Remdesivir (瑞德西韋）及Dexamethasone (地塞米松&ndash;超繽紛怪異的名字)。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">各式化合物</span>的包括Solube ACE2及AngII等等，某程度上亦可界定為藥物。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一個Post粗略講解過人造抗體的最新發展，今個Post將會講解藥物發展的最新狀況，尤其在老藥新用(Drug Repurposing)方面之上。<br />\n<br />\n抵抗武肺的黑馬&ndash;人造抗體<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2141521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2141521</a><br />\n<br />\n老藥新用並唔係新穎概念，最為與人類生活相關的其中一隻，就係生髮洗頭水裡的Minoxidil。本來Minoxidil的主要用途為抗高血壓用，但輾轉之下發現竟然具有促進頭髮生長的效果，所以亦變成為增髮藥物之一。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，用來醫治武肺的Remdesivir (瑞德西韋)原本是Gilead Science針對伊波拉病毒(Ebola)所研發的藥物，但結果並不理想。<br />\n後來Remdesivir被發現能夠有效抑制中東呼吸綜合征冠狀病毒(MERS)在在細胞上的繁殖，科學家便因而嘗試利用它來對抗武肺，發現同樣能抑壓武肺在細胞裡的繁殖。<br />\n<br />\n最近袁教授同美國嗰邊合作發表一份《Nature》文章，在約12000藥物中，搵到21隻能夠增強Remdesivir阻礙武肺生長的效果。(Ref1)<br />\n換句話說，若果將21隻藥物內其中一隻與Remdesivir一同使用的話，就可以降低Remdesivir劑量濃度的同時亦能達到治理效果，變相能夠減低Remdesivir產生副作用的機會。<br />\n<br />\n暫時來說，所有結果均來自實驗室細胞研究。<br />\n如果兩隻藥一齊運用的話，會否真的是對人體產生正面作用，又或者會產生出新的副作用，仍是未知之數。<br />\n<br />\n不過現時當務之急是解決武肺，基本上所有事物都會「開捷徑」同步進行。而就在8月5日，一批科學家發批學術文章(Ref2)利用AI技術設立一套名為Synthia的軟件，更成功為11隻相信能醫治武肺的藥物找出一套更便宜更有效率的合成方法，方便藥廠商可以用更低的成本大量製造藥物（雖然廠商未必會因而調低價格，反之.......）。<br />\n<br />\n只可惜的是，就算套用了他們的AI軟件，依然沒能找出一種比現時Gilead Science釀製Remdesivir的更好方法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2577-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-020-2577-1&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=6741c14c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2577-1</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://chemrxiv.org/articles/preprint/Reinforcing_the_Supply_Chain_of_COVID-19_Therapeutics_with_Expert-Coded_Retrosynthetic_Software/12765410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchemrxiv.org%2Farticles%2Fpreprint%2FReinforcing_the_Supply_Chain_of_COVID-19_Therapeutics_with_Expert-Coded_Retrosynthetic_Software%2F12765410&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=07aa72c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chemrxiv.org/articles/preprint/Reinforcing_the_Supply_Chain_of_COVID-19_Therapeutics_with_Expert-Coded_Retrosynthetic_Software/12765410</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:36:35.000Z","msg":"乜今次咁早啊外國勢力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國勢力係唔會俾你估到的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9f19a62c83c49f534ef2a617fef21a253fb093","tid":2146002,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2de2a043854e2157216b7692559e3e8a89eba64f","tid":2146002,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:44:11.000Z","msg":"地塞米松好似係類固醇既一種？<br />\n我以前皮膚生野去睇醫生，開過地塞米松藥膏比我，一試即見效"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但應該武肺重症出現免疫系統過盛問題，先會有效。"},{"pid":"8b654585a4f7df14da2891b51e213c7f376ca150","tid":2146002,"uid":155238,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"巧掛住薯仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6875e7702d125b21735a9e411084984d0f6a25","tid":2146002,"uid":38861,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8b654585a4f7df14da2891b51e213c7f376ca150","tid":2146002,"uid":155238,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"巧掛住薯仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長遠應該寫科普嘢為主，啲時間好用啲，同埋對自己都有益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629b10ada615fa7d061b93d1caf107839913149b","tid":2146002,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ae9f19a62c83c49f534ef2a617fef21a253fb093","tid":2146002,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2de2a043854e2157216b7692559e3e8a89eba64f","tid":2146002,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:44:11.000Z","msg":"地塞米松好似係類固醇既一種？<br />\n我以前皮膚生野去睇醫生，開過地塞米松藥膏比我，一試即見效"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但應該武肺重症出現免疫系統過盛問題，先會有效。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:32:35.000Z","msg":"2003 SARS爆發時，未似而家有咁多antiviral drug，當時d醫生好似都係靠落steroid<br />\n因為咁所以SARS康復者先咁多後遺症(有錯請指正)"},{"pid":"58862be54d1fe7c715f40bd833e880a3c6fb0359","tid":2146002,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"629b10ada615fa7d061b93d1caf107839913149b","tid":2146002,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ae9f19a62c83c49f534ef2a617fef21a253fb093","tid":2146002,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2de2a043854e2157216b7692559e3e8a89eba64f","tid":2146002,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:44:11.000Z","msg":"地塞米松好似係類固醇既一種？<br />\n我以前皮膚生野去睇醫生，開過地塞米松藥膏比我，一試即見效"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但應該武肺重症出現免疫系統過盛問題，先會有效。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:32:35.000Z","msg":"2003 SARS爆發時，未似而家有咁多antiviral drug，當時d醫生好似都係靠落steroid<br />\n因為咁所以SARS康復者先咁多後遺症(有錯請指正)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:34:48.000Z","msg":"我問過啲醫生，其實嗰時唔係有好多個案有用steroid。"},{"pid":"6216c28b611146a9e6467663d027d49e0593f6dd","tid":2146002,"uid":50366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"繽紛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eddb484c9e0aad9f7900e6f439132332f3c4dff","tid":2146002,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c6875e7702d125b21735a9e411084984d0f6a25","tid":2146002,"uid":38861,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8b654585a4f7df14da2891b51e213c7f376ca150","tid":2146002,"uid":155238,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"